*ppc-sources-2.4.24-r1 (19 Feb 2004)

  19 Feb 2004; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ppc-sources-2.4.24-r1.ebuild,
  files/ppc-sources-2.4.24.munmap.patch:
  Added the patch for the mremap/munmap vulnerability. Bug #42024.

